    :param transform_callback: Keyword-only argument. An optional callable that
        receives the EXIF orientation value and returns the
        :py:class:`~PIL.Image.Transpose` method (or a sequence of methods, applied
        in order) to use instead of the default orientation-to-method mapping. If
        the callback returns ``None``, no transposition is applied. If not
        supplied, the default mapping is used.
